name: Handmade eco-friendly traditional handicraft papercutting - Proposal
description:
This is a more western style work.

The love is most treasured emotion for each. And I think to let some one know your love is very important case for the couple. Actually I heard from one of my female friends.

She was proposed. But of course not in this ancient and formal western way, in china, a proposal is not that clearly shown to people's mind. Mostly couples just pay more attention to their wedding ceremony which is regarded as the most important ceremonies of a person.

But I think this moment is such a sweet thing for them, and it's a very serious thing which deserves a good show.

In fact, I made two works about proposal. This is one of them I would like to show you first :)

This work took about 12 hours app in total. I found some info about western proposal online and in my mind this way is a very good way. do you think so?

This work is about 22cm in square. Black papercutting with white background paper . 


Will ship via air mail which takes about 1-2 weeks to go US. 

See more of my works at http://swipxa.etsy.com
